import React from 'react'
import {FormContainer, FormBody, FormLogBox, FormForm, FormH1, FormInputPass, FormInputButton } from './SignupElements'
import { BackendURL }from '../BackendURL'


const SignUp = () => {

    const handleSubmit = (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        console.log(e.target.name.value)
    }
    return (
        <FormBody>
            <FormContainer>
               <FormLogBox>
                    <FormForm onSubmit={handleSubmit}  >
                        <FormH1>Create Account</FormH1>
                        <FormInputPass placeholder="First Name" type="text" value="firstname" autoFocus="autofocus" required="required" />
                        <FormInputPass placeholder="Last Name" type="text" value="lastname" autoFocus="autofocus" required="required" />
                        <FormInputPass placeholder="Email" type="email" value="email" autoFocus="autofocus" required="required" />
                        <FormInputPass placeholder="Password" type="password" value="password" autoFocus="autofocus" required="required" />
                        <FormInputPass placeholder="Confirm Password" type="password" value="password2" autoFocus="autofocus" required="required" />
                        <FormInputButton type="submit" value="Sign me up!" />
                    </FormForm>  
               </FormLogBox>
            </FormContainer>
        </FormBody>
    )
}


export default SignUp
